Interface FileStatusAcceptor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileStatusAcceptor.AcceptAllButSelf, FileStatusAcceptor.AcceptFilesOnly

    public interface FileStatusAcceptor
    Interface to implement by the logic deciding whether to accept a summary entry or path as a valid file or directory.
